{"tid":1956253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首辦遭淋漆 警拘速遞員","createTime":"2020-04-03T05:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T11:35:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc35f19c2ceb3bfc644749b0c6f5fe0a6608d42","tid":1956253,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/Y7KTTVTRGWX6PRDFRLPONG3CPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FY7KTTVTRGWX6PRDFRLPONG3CPE%2F&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=c5052a0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FY7KTTVTRGWX6PRDFRLPONG3CPE%2F&h=d121ed63\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/Y7KTTVTRGWX6PRDFRLPONG3CPE/</a><br />\n<br />\n特首辦遭淋漆 警拘速遞員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200403/large/1585845496_903e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200403%2Flarge%2F1585845496_903e.jpg&h=661dae64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特首辦外牆遭潑上黑色油漆。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首辦外牆日前遭人淋潑漆油，一名中年男子昨日被捕，警方懷疑他與去年另外四宗公眾地方被噴黑漆案有關，男子正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子姓李（54歲），周一清晨一名工人發現特首辦外牆遭潑上黑色油漆，同日下午2時許，再有職員於附近發現玻璃碎片。警方初步調查後，懷疑案發有人於上周六將盛載黑色油漆的玻璃樽擲向特首辦外牆，案件交由中區警區重案組調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方進一步調查後，昨日於大埔以涉嫌刑事毀壞拘捕姓李男子，據悉，男子任職速遞員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑涉多宗刑毀案<br />\n<br />\n警員於被捕男子住所撿獲同類形玻璃樽及黑色噴罐，懷疑該名男子與去年5月19日分別發生於西區及中區，去年5月27日發生於大埔，以及去年6月7日發生於沙田區兩宗涉及公共設施的刑事毀壞案有關。<br />\n<br />\n2018年11月，一名85歲老翁以白色噴漆於特首辦4號閘外牆壁，寫上「鄭月娥包庇凶犯，葵涌醫院傷天害理」字句，涉嫌刑事毀壞當場被捕，老翁被判罪成，遭罰款100元。"},{"pid":"e2d26f0c333eb01ea71d39b7b8385afc71c89cb1","tid":1956253,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:19:33.000Z","msg":"油漆彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffefc8b3d840ae4d76d663de6739b903b608dae3","tid":1956253,"uid":228868,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:20:34.000Z","msg":"&rsquo;&ldquo;警員於被捕男子住所撿獲同類形玻璃樽及黑色噴罐，懷疑該名男子與去年5月19日分別發生於西區及中區，去年5月27日發生於大埔，以及去年6月7日發生於沙田區兩宗涉及公共設施的刑事毀壞案有關。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15382861a011b47dd0dd089a8056ee7191cd1bad","tid":1956253,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:22:01.000Z","msg":"仲要重案組出嚟調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85f75aec44d3fd26b3da4cc6ca16ae8d298b55b","tid":1956253,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15382861a011b47dd0dd089a8056ee7191cd1bad","tid":1956253,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:22:01.000Z","msg":"仲要重案組出嚟調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:23:14.000Z","msg":"寫「習近平去死」都要出重案"},{"pid":"6a7453bfb30909f41395bc96a818e7c55da2ef42","tid":1956253,"uid":146934,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qn4ccv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQn4ccv1.jpg&h=35b8e350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我啲精都多過佢啲油漆"},{"pid":"a1dde31a427cb86de520910f03b857a973484602","tid":1956253,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:34:36.000Z","msg":"清潔工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ac32e8f207f773ce5583b13056733a91e954c7","tid":1956253,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"噴少少野 大驚小怪 真係垃圾黎"},{"pid":"c1ac29df3fedb57a95f76b3f9fd1ee99010f1e5e","tid":1956253,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"抹得甩就唔係刑事